         This command will create a file named _r_o_o_t._T_A_G_S  in  the
         current  directory.  The file will contain references to
         all Erlang source files in the Erlang distribution.

       * _t_a_g_s:_f_i_l_e_s(["_f_o_o._e_r_l", "_b_a_r._e_r_l", "_b_a_z._e_r_l"],  [{_o_u_t_d_i_r,
